{"TopicId":209142,"ForumId":112,"TopicTitle":"Suggestion for KSP 2\u0027s development: Please Respect Your Health, Intercept Games!","CreatedByName":"intelliCom","CreatedById":209738,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-07-29T11:42:44Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"intelliCom","CreatedById":209738,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-07-29T11:42:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003EI know this is going to be a little bit off-topic compared to the main purpose of this forum, but I haven\u0027t seen people saying this enough. For the mods, I\u0027m sorry in advance if this seems like junk:\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDear Intercept Games,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EDon\u0027t sacrifice your health in favour of getting KSP 2 out.\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTake breaks, and respect your sleep schedule.\u003Cbr\u003E\nEat well, and keep up your fluids.\u003Cbr\u003E\nStaring at a bright screen in the dark damages your sight, so remember to lower the brightness.\u003Cbr\u003E\nDon\u0027t neglect to catch up with friends and family.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd, above all, be happy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-07-29T11:46:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAand this is probably going to be closed like any other post mentioning private life/looks of devs. We\u0027ve been here before.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEdit: oh well\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022giphy.gif\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002275.00\u0022 height=\u0022375\u0022 width=\u0022500\u0022 src=\u0022https://media3.giphy.com/media/a93jwI0wkWTQs/giphy.gif\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-07-29T15:22:34Z\u0022 title=\u002207/29/2022 03:22  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 29, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by The Aziz\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pthigrivi","CreatedById":105624,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-07-29T11:46:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHaving worked more than 50 hours already this week to prep for 3 presentations in as many days I fully concur.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:confused:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_huh.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:confused:\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"intelliCom","CreatedById":209738,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-07-29T13:53:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224158984\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022209142\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221659095167\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150811\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Aziz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, The Aziz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAand this is probably going to be closed like any other post mentioning private life/looks of devs. We\u0027ve been here before.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI believe the closest rule in the guidelines to what you\u0027re mentioning here is 2.2p; \u0022[Do not make posts] demanding or pressuring for release dates or updates from Take-Two or content creators.\u0022\u003Cbr\u003E\nI\u0027m doing the opposite to this, but if I have broken a rule, I will admit my fault.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-07-29T13:54:24Z\u0022 title=\u002207/29/2022 01:54  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 29, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by intelliCom\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ghostii_Space","CreatedById":218794,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-07-29T15:15:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/209738-intellicom/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022209738\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/209738-intellicom/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@intelliCom\u003C/a\u003E! One of devs shared your post with the team, and we want to thank you for appreciating our hard work and dedication. We love KSP2 and we love our players!\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 loading=\u0022lazy\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"darthgently","CreatedById":204885,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-07-29T16:05:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can think of multiple prior posts to these forums that push far into rule 2.2p territory.\u00A0 \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/209738-intellicom/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022209738\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/209738-intellicom/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@intelliCom\u003C/a\u003E\u0027s post doesn\u0027t even come close to having an issue there and is a breath of fresh air, tbh\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-07-31T16:51:47Z\u0022 title=\u